'''Moringa''' ({{lang-en|Moringa oleifera}}, {{lang-ar|البان أو المورنغا}}) waa geed ka baxa dhulka diiran ama kulul ee aasiya iyo afrika geedkaan ayaa magacyo badan loo yaqaan hasw ahaate waxaa ugu caansan magaca ''Moringa  ''waa geed kumanaan sano loo soo isticmaali jiray siyaabo kala duwan, cunno ahaan iyo daawo ahaanba.
Waa geed la sheego inuu leeyahay boqolaal faa'ido oo aan halkaan lagu soo koobi karin, waana geed aad loogu sameeyay baaritaano cilmibaaris oo kaal duwan, haba u badnaan baaritaanandaas in lagu tijaabiyay xayawaanka. geedkaan ayaa wxuu daawo u yahay cudurrada oo dhan wuxuuna la dagaaldaa dhamaan bagteeriyada nool ee dhibta noolaha oo dhan, sida uu daawo ugu yahay nafaqo daarrada iyo abateedka wuxuu leeyahay fiitamiinno ka nooc ah oo aad u badan, waxaa ku jira 7 jibaar fitaminka laga helo liinta iyo afar jibaar fiitamiin Aga la ga helo karootada iyo afar jibaar kaalshimyamka laga helo caanaha<ref name="leone">{{Template:Cite journal|journal=Int J Mol Sci|year=2015|volume=16|issue=6|pages=12791-835|doi=10.3390/ijms160612791|title=Cultivation, Genetic, Ethnopharmacology, Phytochemistry and Pharmacology of Moringa oleifera Leaves: An Overview|vauthors=Leone A, Spada A, Battezzati A, Schiraldi A, Aristil J, Bertoli S|pmid=26057747|url=http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC4490473/}}</ref>.<ref name="GRIN">{{Template:Cite web|url=http://www.ars-grin.gov/cgi-bin/npgs/html/taxon.pl?24597|title=USDA GRIN Taxonomy}}</ref><ref name="GRIN" />




== Tilamaan ==
